title: IAA Tonight | LeBron's Latest Comments on 'The Shop'
description: LeBron James shined in his return to the Drew League since 2011. Find out if Ashley Nicole Moss, Adam Pacman Jones and LeSean McCoy were impressed with his performance. The Lakers star also made some headlines by calling Celtics fans racist and being all in as a teammate on the latest installement of Uninterrupted's 'The Shop'. Is there some validity in his comments?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Ashley Nicole Moss, Adam Pacman Jones, LeSean McCoy)
